Package com.rshepard.atm

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    This class creates a virtual bank account with the typical information.
    BankValidation
    Creates a virtual bank that stores account numbers, PINs, and a current account that is utilized by the Processor class for balance queries, validation, and transactions.
    Command
    Objects of type Command are used to store data that is passed from the Gui to the GuiController.
    DebugScreen
    Debug Screen displays account numbers, PINs, and balances used for the process of debugging when the ATM boots up
    Gui  
    GuiController
    GuiController listens for and sends input from the user on GUI to the Processor class of the ATM
    Logger
    Logger class is used for logging ATM actions and generating receipts one per customer.
    Processor
    Processor class creates and handles the GUI, Controller, Bank, Logger, and Commands input by the user for the ATM
    Start  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Selection
    Selection Enum used to classify selections made by the user
